        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2e0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:32:09.575+09:00">Wishing to base tax payments on landholdings,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-04T01:09:04.92+09:00">Jì Kāngzǐ sent Rǎn Yǒu冉有396 to consult with Kǒngzǐ on the matter.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:32:36.949+09:00">Kǒngzǐ made no reply.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:32:47.027+09:00">Later, he took Rǎn Yǒu aside and said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:32:56.129+09:00">“Come Qiú求!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:33:16.919+09:00">Have you never heard what I am to say?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:33:30.39+09:00">The former kings, in their governance of the men ofservice,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:33:49.899+09:00">based land allotments on their strength</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:33:58.818+09:00">and made their distances equal.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-04T06:00:50.974+09:00">In fixing the tax rates of merchants’ districts,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:34:14.079+09:00">they weighed their relative wealth.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-04T06:01:43.957+09:00">In determining what quantities of corvée laborers to requisition,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:34:39.131+09:00"> they took care to omit the old and weak,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-04T06:00:40.896+09:00">among whom were widowers, widows, orphans, and ill people.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:36:09.254+09:00">When troops were to be raised</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:36:22.9+09:00">otherwise they stopped the levies.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:36:16.231+09:00">they levied taxes;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:36:33.649+09:00">In years with warfare,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:36:47.788+09:00">the amount taken from each well field</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:36:52.666+09:00">was one zōng 稯 of grain,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:36:59.236+09:00">one bǐng 秉 of fodder,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:37:06.701+09:00">and one fǒu ⽸ of rice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:38:43.88+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:37:40.786+09:00">The former kingsconsidered this sufficient.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:37:48.765+09:00"> If Master Jìsūn wants to come up with tax regulations,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:37:57.902+09:00">the records ofZhōu are there.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:38:12.862+09:00">If he wants to act contrary to the regulations,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:38:20.142+09:00">levy taxes in whatever way hepleases.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:38:22.99+09:00">What need is there to consult me about it!”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_006-33a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-01T16:57:07.911+09:00">“But now my lord, you, who perhaps lack something of Wǔ Dīng,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_006-33a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-01T16:57:24.623+09:00">dislike listening to admonitions—is this not an impossible case?”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-216a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-16T04:00:46.537+09:00">Xì Zhì said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-216a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-16T04:00:50.158+09:00">“It can’t be done.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-216a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-16T04:01:46.339+09:00">I have heard</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-216a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-16T04:01:50.083+09:00"> that a fighting man does not rebel,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-216a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-16T04:02:59.049+09:00">that awise man is not duplicitous,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_004-216a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-01-16T04:02:17.661+09:00">and that a virtuous man does not form factions.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
